    <a id="main-content"></a>
            		<h1 class="title" id="page-title">Tours</h1>
                        <div class="block block-system block-main block-system-main odd block-without-title" id="block-system-main">
  <div class="block-inner clearfix">
                
    <div class="content clearfix">
      <article about="/tours" typeof="sioc:Item foaf:Document" class="node node-page node-published node-not-promoted node-not-sticky author-jesse even clearfix" id="node-page-2135">
        <span property="dc:title" content="Tours" class="rdf-meta element-hidden"></span><span property="sioc:num_replies" content="0" datatype="xsd:integer" class="rdf-meta element-hidden"></span>    
  
  <div class="content clearfix">
    <span class="print-link"></span><div class="field field-name-body field-type-text-with-summary field-label-hidden"><div class="field-items"><div class="field-item even" property="content:encoded"> <p>Welcome to Riot Tours!</p>
<p>When we made the move to our <a href="http://www.riotgames.com/articles/20150423/1660/%E2%80%98twas-night-our-move-la" target="_blank">new headquarters in West Los Angeles</a>, we received lots of requests to visit the space. We took some time to settle in and spiff up the joint, and now we&rsquo;re excited to welcome players to our digs. The tour explores Riot culture, and includes a look at how League and the community influenced the design of our campus.</p>
<p>We launched player tours into beta mode in February and it&rsquo;s been a great experience so far! While we&rsquo;re getting our sea legs, there&rsquo;ll be a limited number of dates available, so keep an eye out for more information.</p>
<p>To sign up for a tour, just select the date you&rsquo;re interested in and answer a few questions. Once you submit your request, you&rsquo;ll receive a registration confirmation within three business days. If tours are full, or available dates don&rsquo;t fit into your schedule, don&rsquo;t worry! We&rsquo;ll release additional dates during the first week of each month, so check back often.</p>
<p>For further information about tours, check out the <a href="http://www.riotgames.com/tours/faqs" target="_blank">Tours FAQ</a>.</p>
<p class="c-tour-header__text"><a class="btn c-btn--tour" href="/tours/schedule" style="text-align: center;">Tour Schedule</a></p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
 </div></div></div>  </div>
  
  <div class="clearfix">
          <nav class="links node-links clearfix"></nav>
    
      </div>
</article>    </div>
  </div>
</div><section class="block block-webform c-tours-updates-form block-client-block-2138 block-webform-client-block-2138 even" id="block-webform-client-block-2138">
  <div class="block-inner clearfix">
              <h2 class="block-title">Riot Tours Updates</h2>
            
    <div class="content clearfix">
      <article about="/riot-tours-updates" typeof="sioc:Item foaf:Document" class="node node-webform node-published node-not-promoted node-not-sticky author-jesse odd clearfix" id="node-webform-2138">
        <header>
    <h2 class="node-title"><a href="/riot-tours-updates" title="Riot Tours Updates">Riot Tours Updates</a></h2>
  </header>
    <span property="dc:title" content="Riot Tours Updates" class="rdf-meta element-hidden"></span><span property="sioc:num_replies" content="0" datatype="xsd:integer" class="rdf-meta element-hidden"></span>    
  
  <div class="content clearfix">
    <span class="print-link"></span><div class="field field-name-body field-type-text-with-summary field-label-hidden"><div class="field-items"><div class="field-item even" property="content:encoded"> <p>Fill out the form below to recieve news and updates about Riot Games tours.</p>

neste sábado, dia 25,  às 15h e vai até o dia 22 de abril. Para começar, o Buxixo da Van realizará sua próxima edição neste sábado no Pollito.     <a id="main-content"></a>
            		<h1 class="title" id="page-title">Forbes profiles Riot passion</h1>
                        <div class="block block-system block-main block-system-main odd block-without-title" id="block-system-main">
  <div class="block-inner clearfix">
                
    <div class="content clearfix">
      


<article about="/articles/20121015/241/forbes-profiles-riot-passion" typeof="sioc:Item foaf:Document" class="node node-article node-published node-not-promoted node-not-sticky author-bsnyder odd clearfix" id="node-article-241">
        <span property="dc:title" content="Forbes profiles Riot passion" class="rdf-meta element-hidden"></span><span property="sioc:num_replies" content="0" datatype="xsd:integer" class="rdf-meta element-hidden"></span>	  
    
    <div class="post-date">Posted on 10-15-12</div>		
		<div class="share-bar">
			<a class="print_ico" href="/print/articles/20121015/241/forbes-profiles-riot-passion">Print</a>
			<!-- <a class="pdf_ico" href="/printpdf/articles/20121015/241/forbes-profiles-riot-passion">PDF</a> -->
			<span class='st_email_custom st_ico' displayText='Email'></span>

  <div class="content clearfix">
    <div class="field field-name-body field-type-text-with-summary field-label-hidden"><div class="field-items"><div class="field-item even" property="content:encoded"> <p>We opened the doors to our Santa Monica digs for press from around the world in the days leading up to the <a href="/articles/20121017/549/league-legends-season-two-championship" target="_blank"><em>League of Legends&nbsp;</em>Season Two World Championship</a> in Los Angeles.<em> Forbes.com</em>&#39;s&nbsp;Paul Tassi shared his thoughts on the day&#39;s experiences, saying:</p>
<p>&quot;<em>There&#39;s an almost obsessive drive to keep adding value [for] players, something Riot believes is crucial to their success and, really, is their entire company philosophy.&quot;</em></p>
<p><a href="http://www.forbes.com/sites/insertcoin/2012/10/15/league-of-legends-championships-prove-riot-is-on-top-of-the-world/" target="_blank">Flip over to <em>Forbes.com</em> </a>for the whole story.</p>
<p><a href="http://www.forbes.com/sites/insertcoin/2012/10/15/league-of-legends-championships-prove-riot-is-on-top-of-the-world/" target="_blank"><img alt="" src="/sites/default/files/uploads/Forbes-BabySuperman_0.jpg" style="width: 656px; height: 650px; " /></a></p>
 </div></div></div>

    <div class="field field-name-body field-type-text-with-summary field-label-hidden"><div class="field-items"><div class="field-item even" property="content:encoded"> <p>Riot Games was established in 2006 by entrepreneurial gamers who believe that player-focused game development can result in great games. In 2009, Riot released its debut title<em> League of Legends</em> to critical and player acclaim. As the most played video game in the world, over 67 million play every month. Players form the foundation of our community and it’s for them that we continue to evolve and improve the <em>League of Legends </em>experience.</p></div></div></div>  </div>
  
  <div class="clearfix">
          <nav class="links node-links clearfix"><ul class="links inline"><li class="node-readmore first last"><a href="/careers/information-security-engineer-0" rel="tag" title="Information Security Engineer">Read more<span class="element-invisible"> about Information Security Engineer</span></a></li></ul></nav>
    
      </div>

                        data: json,
                        debug: false
                    });
                }
            });
        });
    }

        realtime(realtimeLoaded, "onLoad");
        realtimeLoaded = true;
    })

        realtime(realtimeLoaded, "timeout")
        realtimeLoaded = true;
    }, 3000);

                    </a>

        <div class="content right relative">
        
            <p class="date">24.03.2017</p>
            <h1 class="l-title l-title-m">
                <a href="http://financasfemininas.uol.com.br/como-investir-pensando-na-aposentadoria-sem-depender-do-inss/" class="post-link" title="Como investir pensando na aposentadoria sem depender do INSS">
                    Como investir pensando na aposentadoria sem depender do INSS                </a>
            </h1>
            <p class="cat"><a href='http://financasfemininas.uol.com.br/investimento/como-comecar/' class=''>Como começar?</a></p>
            <p>
                <a href="http://financasfemininas.uol.com.br/como-investir-pensando-na-aposentadoria-sem-depender-do-inss/" class="post-link" title="Com a reforma da previdência, não dá mais para depender do INSS para se aposentar. O Primo Rico ensina como investir para ter um futuro tranquilo.">
                    Com a reforma da previdência, não dá mais para depender do INSS para se aposentar. O Primo Rico ensina como investir para ter um futuro tranquilo.                </a>
            </p>

                <p>Quem está de mudança, precisa encarar o desafio de mobiliar um apartamento. Confira dicas para economizar nessas compras e não prejudicar o orçamento. </p>
            </a>

        </td><td class="ge-card-classificacao-col ge-card-classificacao-sigla">
            {{if link}}
                <a href="${link}" alt="${equipe.nome_popular}" title="${equipe.nome_popular}" >
            {{/if}}
                ${equipe.sigla}
            {{if link}}
                </a>
            {{/if}}
        </td><td class="ge-card-classificacao-col ge-card-classificacao-variacao"><div class="ge-card-classificacao-variacao"><span>${variacao}</span><span class="sprite-variacao sprite-${variacao_label}"></span></div></td><td class="ge-card-classificacao-col ge-card-classificacao-pontos">${ pontos }</td><td class="ge-card-classificacao-col ge-card-classificacao-vitorias">${ vitorias }</td><td class="ge-card-classificacao-col ge-card-classificacao-saldo">${ saldo_gols }</td></tr></script><script>
$(document).ready(function() {
    "use strict";

    if($('.glb-grid-24')){

        var cardId = '#ge-card-classificacao-bd4d78ae-5ae2-4f18-b987-b004288e85c6',
                classificacaoFeedReady = false,
                classificacaoCardReady = false;

            $(document).on('bastian-feed-card_rendered', cardId, function() {
                console.debug('Classificacao: Feed Ready');
                classificacaoFeedReady = true;
                initCardClassificacao();
            });

            $(document).on('card-classificacao-ready', function() {
                console.debug('Classificacao: Card Ready');
                classificacaoCardReady = true;
                initCardClassificacao();
            });

        var initCardClassificacao = function(){
            if(classificacaoCardReady && classificacaoFeedReady){
                $('#ge-card-classificacao-bd4d78ae-5ae2-4f18-b987-b004288e85c6').show();
            }
        }
    }

    try {

      var classificacao = new CardClassificacao({
        context: '#ge-card-classificacao-bd4d78ae-5ae2-4f18-b987-b004288e85c6'
      });

      var classificacaoTracking = new CardClassificacaoTracking("bd4d78ae-5ae2-4f18-b987-b004288e85c6");

    } catch (err) {}

});

    var glb_realtime_map = {
        site: 'globoesporte',
        categories: ['home'],
        url: 'http://globoesporte.globo.com/rn/'
    };

    var realtime = function(realtimeLoaded, msg){
        if(realtimeLoaded){
            return;
        }

        $.getScript('http://s.glbimg.com/bu/rt/js/glb-rt.js', function(){
            $.ajax({
                dataType: 'jsonp',
                
                url: 'http://s.glbimg.com/es/ge/static/live/globoesporte/json/globoesporte-home-agregador.js',
                
                jsonpCallback: 'glbrealtime_callback',
                cache: true,
                success: function(json){
                    $.glbrealtime({
                        data: json,
                        debug: false
                    });
                }
            });
        });
    }

    var realtimeLoaded = false;

    $(window).on('load', function(){
        realtime(realtimeLoaded, "onLoad");
        realtimeLoaded = true;
    })

    setTimeout(function(){
        realtime(realtimeLoaded, "timeout")
        realtimeLoaded = true;
    }, 3000);

</script><link rel="stylesheet"
